neighbourhood_group_cleansed: Welcome to Coyoacán neighborhood! Coyoacan preserves many of the great city planning features of the colonial times: cobblestone streets, multiple plazas to sit on a bench and relax, trees everywhere, the traditional market (El Mercado), colonial mansions with colorful facades now converted to art galleries or cultural centers. In a nutshell, Coyoacan has the feeling of a little town in the middle of the Megalopolis. Even better, you can access other parts of the town via the subway, buses or uber.
